begin BILL_TT_Tanusea_Veloth
; quest behaveour for TT_DiseaseCarrier quest
; basically checks to see if she's been killed

; script location: should be placed on Tanusea Veloth

; variables

if ( MenuMode == 1 )
	return
endif

if ( OnDeath == 1 )
	; when we are killed...
	if ( GetJournalIndex "TT_DiseaseCarrier" > 0 )
		; ... and if the player is on the quest ...
		Player->Journal "TT_DiseaseCarrier" 40		; killed us
	endif
endif

end BILL_TT_Tanusea_Veloth
